<h1>Choose a class below to start learning.</h1>

<p>If you are new to computers, haven't used them for a while, are a little unsure and uncomfortable, or just need a bit of a refresher, we have the tools to help you tackle technology at your own pace and gain the confidence you need to succeed.</p>

<% @courses.each_with_index do |c, index| %>
  <% if index % 3 == 0 %>
    <div class="row">
  <% end %>

    <div class="four-col<% if index % 3 == 2 %> last<% end %>">
      <a class="course-widget" href="<%= course_path(c) %>">
        <header>
          <h3 style="background: url('http://digitallearn.org/sites/default/files/class_topics/basic_skills_0.png') no-repeat scroll right 5px transparent"><%= c.title %></h3>
        </header>
        <div class="description">
          <p><%= c.summary %></p>
          <p class="duration">15 mins</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

  <% if index % 3 == 2 %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

<% end %>